description:
Prepare to witness the regal presence of Sekhar, Fang of Nulahmia, as she takes centre stage in this showcase post. Follow along my painting guides to capture the essence of Sekhar's dark allure and her serpentine companion, Ouboroth, painted to match my Legion of Blood and Nighthaunt collection.

The post Showcase: Soulblight Gravelords Sekhar, Fang of Nuhlamia (inc. paint recipes) appeared first on Tale of Painters.
title: Showcase: Soulblight Gravelords Sekhar, Fang of Nuhlamia (inc. paint recipes)
